des:
Alexa and the eWiseHome products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.If you have any problem when use this skill, please contact us via support@ewisehome.net

Steps of setup.
1. Download the eWiseHome app;
2. Register an eWiseHome account;
3. Configure a device in eWiseHome app and set an appropriate name for the device which will be used for voice control;
4. Download Amazon Alexa app;
5. Search eWiseHome skill within Amazon Alexa app;
6. Enable eWiseHome skill and you'll be navigated to eWiseHome login page;
7. Input your eWiseHome account’s username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
8. Now setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control like:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
